  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game introduction:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/0a4da37c6fc83d047a66187790ab31c1.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yase Yuichi, an ordinary college student, wakes up from an unknown laboratory, along with eight people who do not know each other. They are then told by a mysterious man wearing a skull mask with a sheep's head that they will be involved in a game of judging to the death. Three of the nine are not humans, but bionic people who will kill humans, and what they have to do is to correctly find the Bionic people hiding in the nine people and execute them, otherwise human beings will be killed by Bionic people. What future will the nine people in danger face?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/2d78d095198ea3af63f7439277be4a78.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plot: The main line is divided into three chapters, each containing a tense and thrilling story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/e50161bbc1b36c7b6a8facb0e510eb88.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters: 9 characters with distinctive personalities that you can not only keep company with, but also have free dates with them in your leisure time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/cb1cfba9f945f38c81ab8316b633e9b1.avif?t=1750181509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras_big/cb1cfba9f945f38c81ab8316b633e9b1.avif?t=1750181509 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scene: Simple and simple scene with rich interactive eggs waiting for you to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/ec9d3a724695285e3725ebf5c84adb1c.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG: Contains rich scene CG images to increase the immersion of your play.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game introduction:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/0a4da37c6fc83d047a66187790ab31c1.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yase Yuichi, an ordinary college student, wakes up from an unknown laboratory, along with eight people who do not know each other. They are then told by a mysterious man wearing a skull mask with a sheep's head that they will be involved in a game of judging to the death. Three of the nine are not humans, but bionic people who will kill humans, and what they have to do is to correctly find the Bionic people hiding in the nine people and execute them, otherwise human beings will be killed by Bionic people. What future will the nine people in danger face?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/2d78d095198ea3af63f7439277be4a78.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plot: The main line is divided into three chapters, each containing a tense and thrilling story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/e50161bbc1b36c7b6a8facb0e510eb88.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters: 9 characters with distinctive personalities that you can not only keep company with, but also have free dates with them in your leisure time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/cb1cfba9f945f38c81ab8316b633e9b1.avif?t=1750181509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras_big/cb1cfba9f945f38c81ab8316b633e9b1.avif?t=1750181509 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scene: Simple and simple scene with rich interactive eggs waiting for you to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406150/extras/ec9d3a724695285e3725ebf5c84adb1c.avif?t=1750181509\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG: Contains rich scene CG images to increase the immersion of your play.</p>",
